      "writtenOn": "2020-03-27T22:47:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Most external users of the emulator expect Swiftshader to always be used when -no-window is used. We\u0027ve already had some highly visible bugs due to the expectation. It should be documented, yes. This sentence also could use some clarification; if no -gpu flag is used, it\u0027s as if -gpu auto was passed on the command line, unless overriden in avd config.ini",
      "parentUuid": "432f23bb_53da0e48",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 13,
        "startChar": 6,
        "endLine": 14,
        "endChar": 28
      },
      "revId": "758ee87c358d114fafb46d98b6be7f0ade6895af",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
