      },
      "lineNbr": 14,
      "author": {
        "id": 1125918
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-30T18:10:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think we should do that. This could break existing users that are relying on \"-gpu auto -nowindow\" --\u003e swiftshader. \n\nI will update the documentation in the commit message. Let me know if the -help needs updating as that is very specific.",
      "parentUuid": "cfbf1c94_b4e5ee09",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 13,
        "startChar": 6,
