      "writtenOn": "2020-03-30T18:15:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e This could break existing users that are relying on \"-gpu auto -nowindow\" --\u003e swiftshader.\n\nWho are these users? Can they just remove the -gpu auto flag?",
