      "writtenOn": "2020-03-30T18:18:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s also more confusing if we require an additional -gpu auto flag ; that breaks existing logic where -gpu XXXX is applied; -gpu auto should in principle be equivalent to not having a -gpu flag",
